version_description: An intro was added. Some passing chords were added to make the song more melodic. Some of the chords were repositioned to be over the correct words.
This is in the correct key, with the correct words and phrases, you can transpose it as needed and add capos for those of you who can't sing along with the recording.

song_name: Somebody Told Me To Feel Good Somebody Told Me Vs Feel Good Inc
